column3: “The original Millennium OG was created by a breeder in Northern California between 2007-2009 by cross breeding MauiSuperDawg x OG kush x Sour Diesel x Headband.   Topping the charts at 20% THC and 5% CBD the medical quality and asthetics  are sure to satisfy all patients needs.”
“I Really Enjoyed this one. Millennium Falcon strand is in STL. BOMB!”
“Probably the best hybrid I have ever smoked”
“Got this from an Iranian guy. Relaxing but makes me quite paranoid, so -1 star for that.”
“I smoked this and was gonna go on a hike. Made it too the recliner and woke up 4 hours later...:a deep indica too say the least lol. Night time use for me but all around very pleasant”

“I never even heard of this strain. It is a strange and confusing high. One minute I was glued to the furniture then suddenly there were random bursts of energy. I did laugh a lot but the sativa and indica seem to compete constantly for your attention. This one was all over the place but I'd do it again.”
“clean high. helped with arthritis pain but figured out it is certainly a night time bud. gets me tired and very little physical energy or creative thought.”
“easily on my top three with off the charts CBD levels that you can feel almost right away ...”
